metadata.name: Nightmare Or Reality ?
metadata.description:
Nightmare Or Reality ?
His life is very difficult
He has bad dreams every night Terrible nightmares
Everyone thinks that he will not see the morning when he sleeps tonight
 He goes to his bed one night and closes his eyes and thinks about the nightmares of every night
Her mother's husband is moving from the stairs of the house towards the girl's room and the sound of wooden stairs can be heard â€˜ He arrives in front of the girl's room
 He opens the room door slowly and enters the room
 He sees the girl sleeping deeply on her bed with her back to the door and facing the window
 Dear girl, she has been working like a maid since morning and she has had a hard day and now she is sleeping with a lot of stress and waiting for a new hard day tomorrow.
 And see, I depicted his nightmare tonight
